                                                                            <comments>
                            <comment id="66390" author="linda" created="Wed, 11 Sep 2013 19:15:59 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Fix approved and merged.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="65856" author="linda" created="Thu, 5 Sep 2013 16:57:54 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Second patch submitted and ready for review at &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/7540/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/7540/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="65640" author="linda" created="Tue, 3 Sep 2013 18:21:32 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Change ready for review at &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/7540/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/7540/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="65117" author="niu" created="Tue, 27 Aug 2013 01:53:30 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;yes, this workaround is only needed for old quota architecture (&amp;lt; 2.4).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="65113" author="adilger" created="Tue, 27 Aug 2013 00:42:26 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Niu or Johann, can you please confirm Richard&apos;s comments above?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="59438" author="rhenwood" created="Tue, 28 May 2013 15:49:22 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ve been discussing this topic with Linda: The Manual currently covers the entire 2.x series of Lustre.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I understand this workaround becomes redundant for Lustre 2.4 an beyond. A suitable update to the Manual should include the workaround described here, prepended with something like:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;&amp;lt;note condition=&apos;l24&apos;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;para&amp;gt;This workaround is only needed for versions of Lustre before 2.4 as the bug was fixed in the 2.4 release&amp;lt;/para&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/note&amp;gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</comment>
